oai_dc:dc.dc:title: ANALYSIS OF WAVE FORCES ACTING ON COMBINED CAISSONS WITH INNER SLOPE RUBBLE MOUND
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Faraci, Carla
Liu, Yong
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Combined caisson
slope rubble mound
wave force
semi-analytical solution
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This study examines the horizontal wave forces acting on combined caissons with inner slope rubble mound based on the semi-analytical solution of Liu and Faraci (2014). The calculating method of the horizontal wave forces are presented and validated. The effects of several caisson parameters on the wave forces are shown using some numerical examples. Some useful results are presented for engineering designs.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Coastal Engineering Proceedings; No. 34 (2014): Proceedings of 34th Conference on Coastal Engineering, Seoul, Korea, 2014; structures.51
